hen logging the first mismatch, using `$display` with time markers is crucial. I must ensure the values of the inputs/outputs at that exact clock edge are captured before the simulation advances further.\n- The comparison logic for `tb_match` is complex (`{ out_ref } === ( { out_ref } ^ { out_dut } ^ { out_ref } )`). I will ensure this remains exactly as provided to maintain original functionality.\n\n**Key Change:** The `final` block will be completely rewritten to meet the specified pass/fail criteria, and the `always` block will be augmented to log the first mismatch state.",
